  "text": "In the research [CITATION_1] a combination has been presented and the experimental work has been done with a new approach for the combined recommender system. The recommender systems are traditionally divided into three categories: content-based, collaborative filtering and combined method; the recommender systems have used a combination of both content-based and collaborative filtering methods to obtain better advices and benefit from their advantages.",
